#. module: base_wua
#: model:mail.template,body_html:base_wua.mail_template_data_new_portal_user
msgid "\n"
"                <p>Dear ${object.user_id.name or ''},</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>We have granted access to ${object.wizard_id.portal_id.name} in ${user.company_id.name}.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Your account information is:</p>\n"
"                <ul>\n"
"                <li>User: ${object.user_id.login or ''}</li>\n"
"                <li>Database: ${'dbname' in ctx and ctx['dbname'] or ''}</li>\n"
"                <li>Portal: <a href=\"${'portal_url' in ctx and ctx['portal_url'] or ''}\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">link</a></li>\n"
"                </ul>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"\n"
"                <p><b>You can set or change your password at the following link</b></p>\n"
"                <a href=\"${object.user_id.signup_url}\"\n"
"                    style=\"color:#378167;padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: #FFFFFF; border-color:#378167; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0px; font-weight: 400; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; background-image: none; background-color: #378167; border: 1px solid #378167; border-radius:3px\">\n"
"                    Set password\n"
"                </a>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>${object.wizard_id.welcome_message or ''}</p>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Once the password has been set, you will be able to log in to the e-Office at the <a href=\"${'portal_url' in ctx and ctx['portal_url'] or ''}\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">following address</a>.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>To log in, click on <b>Login</b> and enter your user account ${object.user_id.login or ''}&nbsp;and password.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Once logged in, you will be able to consult the information on your membership card, parcels, invoices, viewer, etc.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>You can consult in more detail the use of the user portal by accessing the following <a href=\"https://wiki.moval.es/Odoo_funcional/administracion_sitio_web/Usuario_de_portal_comunero\">link</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>If you need any further clarification, you can contact the company's office ${user.company_id.name}.</p>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Yours sincerely,</p>\n"
"                <p>${user.company_id.name}</p>\n"
"\n"
"            "
msgstr "\n"
"                <p>Estimado/a ${object.user_id.name or ''},</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Hemos otorgado acceso a ${object.wizard_id.portal_id.name} en ${user.company_id.name}.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Su información de cuenta es:</p>\n"
"                <ul>\n"
"                <li>Usuario: ${object.user_id.login or ''}</li>\n"
"                <li>Base de datos: ${'dbname' in ctx and ctx['dbname'] or ''}</li>\n"
"                <li>Portal: <a href=\"${'portal_url' in ctx and ctx['portal_url'] or ''}\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">enlace</a></li>\n"
"                </ul>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"\n"
"                <p><b>Puede establecer o cambiar su contraseña en el siguiente enlace</b></p>\n"
"                <a href=\"${object.user_id.signup_url}\"\n"
"                    style=\"color:#378167;padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: #FFFFFF; border-color:#378167; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0px; font-weight: 400; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; background-image: none; background-color: #378167; border: 1px solid #378167; border-radius:3px\">\n"
"                    Establecer contraseña\n"
"                </a>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>${object.wizard_id.welcome_message or ''}</p>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Una vez establecida la contraseña podrá entrar a la oficina electrónica en la <a href=\"${'portal_url' in ctx and ctx['portal_url'] or ''}\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">siguiente dirección</a>.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Para entrar debe pinchar en <b>Iniciar sesión</b> e introducir su cuenta de usuario ${object.user_id.login or ''}&nbsp;y la contraseña elegida.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Una vez iniciada la sesión podrá consultar la información de su ficha de socio, parcelas, facturas, visor, etc.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Puede consultar con más detalle el uso del portal de usuario accediendo al siguiente <a href=\"https://wiki.moval.es/Odoo_funcional/administracion_sitio_web/Usuario_de_portal_comunero\">enlace</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Si necesita alguna aclaración adicional, puede ponerse en contacto con la oficina de la ${user.company_id.name}.</p>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"                <br>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Atentamente,</p>\n"
"                <p>${user.company_id.name}</p>\n"
"\n"
"            "

